 <blockquote>


<font color=ff0000 size=+2>Perjury Plea for Former Detective</font>


<BR>


</BLOCKQUOTE>








October 7, 1996<P>


<BLOCKQUUOTE>
<PRE>

<B><B>CRIMINAL LAW & PROCEDURE<P>



[Editor's Note:</B> Mark Fuhrman will serve three years on 

probation in his new home state of Idaho. Prosecutors and Fuhrman, 

a former LAPD Detective, reached this sentencing agreement 

regarding perjury charges. Fuhrman pled nolo contendre to the 

charges stemming from his testimony in the trial of O.J. Simpson 

for the murders of Nicole Brown Simpson and Ron Goldman.]



