<h3 align=center><font color=42426F>Buying and Selling a Law Practice</font></h3> <blockquote>


<P>

This seminar, moderated by Edward Poll, author of  <I>Attorney & Law Firm
Guide to the Business of Law: Planning & Operating for Survival & Growth</I>,
will explore the opportunities and hazards of buying and selling a law
firm. Can you do it legally? Can you do it ethically? How do you value a
law firm for purchase or sale? How do you negotiate the price and other
terms of the sale?

</P>


