<h3 align=center><font color=42426F>MEDIA ROUNDTABLE: A PUBLIC RELATIONS PRIMER FOR LAWYERS  </font></h3> <blockquote>


<H4>September 16 -31 </H4>

<P>Join a panel of public relations and marketing professionals, media members, and lawyers in the
Lawyers Marketing Clinic (RESOURCES) to find out how to get the press your deserve and draw
attention to your practice.  Our panel will examine how lawyers and the media interact and will try
to shed light upon ways to improve the often-times-strained relationship.    </P>

<P><B>Our panel includes:</B> </P>

<P>Steve Flehinger, FMS Marketing, New York (Moderator)  </P>

<P>Alan Bromley, Bromley Group, New York </P>

<P>Karen Dillon, Editor and Publisher, The American Lawyer, New York </P>


<P>Ann Gallagher, Gallagher & Lazarus, Illinois  </P>

<P>Raoul Felder, Raoul Felder, P.C., New York  </P>

<P>Sam Meddis, USA Today, Virginia </P>

<P>Jamie Lisa Moss, JLM Services, Inc., New Jersey  </P>

<P>Jim Lyons, News Editor, Court TV, New York  </P>

<P>Len Tepper, Fox News, New York </P>

<P>Llyod Truffelman, Trylon Communications, New York  </P>

<P>Pete Williams, NBC News, D.C. </P>

<P>Join us with your questions and comments from September 16 - 30.  You'll find this Roundtable in
RESOURCES in the Lawyers Marketing Clinic.  If you have any questions, please call 800-955-5291 and
a Counsel Connect Consultant will be glad to assist you.  </P>




