<h3 align=center><font color=42426F>Smaller Law Firm Leadership Conference</font></h3> 
<blockquote>

<H4>July 22 - August 2</H4>

<P></P>


<P>LIVE:  July 18-19, Hilton Head, SC</P>

<P>ONLINE: July 24 - Aug. 14, Counsel Connect </P>

<P>Is managing your smaller firm an uphill battle? </P>

<P>Fulcrum Informations Services has crafted a new program to address the
unique needs and concerns of law firms with 45 or fewer attorneys.   </P>

<P>You can attend the live seminar at the Westin Hotel on Hilton Head Island
by calling Fulcrum at 1-800-869-4302.  Seminar panelists will come online
after the live program to continue their discussions.  They'll address such
topics as: </P>
<UL>
<P><LI> Maximizing Profitability Through Improved Financial Management </P>

<P><LI> Magnetism in the Marketplace:  Attracting and Keeping the Best Talent </P>

<P><LI> Compensation Strategies for Smaller Firms </P>

<P><LI> Leveraging the Dollars your Firm Invests in Technology </P>

<P><LI> Strategic Planning for the Long Term</P>
</IL>
<P>Fulcrum's Featured Panel Includes:</P>
<IL>
<P>Parry Aftab (Moderator), Aftab & Savitt</P>

<P>Paul S. Anderson, Sonnenberg & Anderson</P>

<P>Richard Bischoff, Gunster, Yoakley, Valdes-Fauli & Stewart </P>

<P>Gerard G. Boccuti, EI DuPont De Nemours and Company </P>

<P>Joel Finger, Roberts & Finger</P>

<P>Joseph A. Fitzpatrick, Fitzpatrick, Lentz & Bubba </P>

<P>Mark L. Gordon, Gordon & Glickson</P>

<P>Stephanie B. Irvine., Pritchett, Cooke & Burch </P>

<P>I. Harold Koretzky, Carver, Darden, Koretzky, Tessier, Finn, Blossman &
Areaux </P>

<P>Todd S. Lundy, Altschuler, Melvoin & Glasser </P>

<P>William H. Myers, Myers Krause & Stevens </P>

<P>David C. Pishko, Elliot, Pishko, Gelbin & Morgan </P>
</UL>
<P>Join the online panel in DISCUSS under Counsel Connect Seminars and Special
Events beginning July 24.  Please call our Customer Service Department if
you have any questions about this program. </P>





