<h3 align=center>Going 
Solo: Opening Your Own Shop</h3> 
<blockquote>
<H4 align=center>May 6 - 17</H4>


<P>Ever thought of hanging out your own shingle?  If you'd like to know whether
you have the personality to succeed as a solo, or if you have already made the
decision to go it alone but need help with the mechanics, this seminar is for
you.  Lawyers who work alone and consultants who advise solos will discuss all
aspects of the solo practice, including how to: draft a business plan and get
financing; set up your office, including hardware, software and staffing
needs; market your practice. Our experts  will also answer your questions.  Due
to 
the nature of the subject, we will offer the option of submitting questions
anonymously.</P>






<h4><a href=/inside/seminars.html><I>Seminars index</I></a></h4>

