<a name=one><h3 align=center>Hofstra Legal Ethics
Conference: The Core Issues</H3></a>

<H4  align=center>Ongoing through April 26</h4>

<blockquote>
Counsel Connect presents the online continuation of Hofstra University School
of Law's third annual seminar on "Legal Ethics: The Core Issues." Counsel
Connect members will have a unique opportunity to interact with some of the
foremost voices in the legal ethics community. 
</P><P>
In assembling its panel, Hofstra University has encouraged these panelists to
step forward with fresh -- and sometimes daring -- perspectives on ethics and
the legal profession. Don't miss it. 
</P>
</blockquote><P>
