<HTML>
<TITLE>ABOUT LAWYER SEARCH</TITLE>
<body>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#008740" ALINK="#008740" VLINK="#4B5548"
TEXT="#002065">
<IMG  valign = top SRC = "/lawyersearch/gallery/eye.gif"><BR>
<IMG valign = top SRC = "/lawyersearch/gallery/aboutls.gif"><BR>
<IMG width = 20 valign = top SRC = "/lawyersearch/gallery/blank.gif">

<!--<IMG valign = top SRC = "/lawyersearch/gallery/aaboutls.gif"><BR>--->

<P>
<IMG valign = top SRC = "/lawyersearch/gallery/whatls.gif"><P>
<UL>Lawyer Search </A>is an electronic directory of lawyers who are <a
href="/inside/about.html">Counsel Connect</a> members. Although it is not a
comprehensive directory of lawyers, it has one key benefit: All
the lawyers listed here are accessible by e-mail. Any listing you find in Lawyer
Search will include the lawyer's e-mail address and a link you can use to send
him or her a  message, instantly.
<P>
The directory is searchable by several categories, including name, firm or
company, city, state, area of expertise, law school, and bar admission (you'd
use
this category if you wanted to find a lawyer in New York who was also licensed
to
practice in California, for example).
<P>
Some listings also include narrative descriptions of the lawyer's experience, as
well as links to other Web sites -- firm home pages, helpful legal resources,
etc.


