<HTML><TITLE>LAWYER SEARCH HELP</TITLE><body><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#008740" ALINK="#008740" VLINK="#4B5548" TEXT="#002065"><IMG width = 505 height = 91 valign = top SRC = "./gallery/helphead.gif"><P><P><IMG ALIGN=left width=35 height=800 SRC="./gallery/spacer.gif">You can use Counsel Connect's Lawyer Search to find lawyers in your region with the specialty you need, or search by name to get more information about a particular lawyer.  And you can send e-mail to the lawyers who fits your search criteria directly from Lawyer Search.</P><P>To search the directory, choose <A HREF=searchby.html>Search the Directory</A> from the main Lawyer Search screen.  Then just fill in the blanks, make choices from the <I>practice area</I> and <I>region</I> lists and click the <I>Search Directory</I> button at the bottom of the screen.</P><IMG SRC = "./gallery/searchin.gif"><p> You don't need to fill in every blank.  Only choose criteria that matter to you.For instance, if you are looking for a products liability lawyer in California, choose<I>Products Liability</I> from the practice area list, and <I>California</I> from the region list, but don't fill out the <I>Law School</I> or <I>Firm or Organization</I>boxes.<P><A NAME="wildcard">In most cases, typing a few key wordsseparated by "and" or "or" will get you the documents you need. However,Lawyer Search also recognizes the more complex Boolean expressions describedbelow. </A><PRE>TYPE                  Finds any profile containing ...------------------------------------------------------------------TAX                    TAXTAX*                   TAX followed by any number of charactersTAX?                   TAX followed by just one character</PRE><I>A <A HREF="detailsr.html">more detailed explanation</A> of Boolean search logic...</I><P>You can clear the search screen and start over by clicking the <I>Clear Search</I> button from the bottom of the window.  (If you are using Netscape Navigator, you shouldclick the <I>New Search</I> icon at the bottom of the screen. Navigator does not handle the <I>ClearSearch</I> button properly.)<P>When your search is completed, your search results will be displayed on your screen. </P><P>If an Internet address is included in a listing, you can send e-mail directly to that lawyer by clicking on his or her Internet address.</P><P><BR><P><CENTER><A HREF="brandbar.map"><IMG border = 0 SRC = "./gallery/ghelpbr.gif" ISMAP></A><BR><p><FONT SIZE = -2><TT>[ <A HREF="welcome.html">Welcome</A> | <A HREF="searchby.html">Search Options</A> | <A HREF="/lsearch/cgi-bin/print_update.cgi">Member Services</A> | <A HREF="aboutls.html">How to Join</A> | <A HREF="help.html">Help</A> ]</UL></TT></FONT SIZE></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
