<BR>
<LI><B>Deborah A. Garza</B> Counsels on mergers,  joint ventures,  technology licensing and distribution issues; represents clients before the Department of Justice and FTC; formerly chief of staff and counselor (1987-1989) and special assistant (1984-1985) to assistant attorney general for antitrust,  U.S. Department of Justice.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Timothy C. Hester</B> Represents clients in complex antitrust litigation; advises on mergers,  joint ventures,  and distribution issues; and specializes in Hart-Scott-Rodino Act matters.<BR>
