<CENTER>
<H2>Antitrust</H2>
<H3>Gray,  Plant,  Mooty,  Mooty  & Bennett,  P.A.
</H3>

</CENTER>
<B><CENTER>Minneapolis:</B> 3400 City Center,  33 South Sixth Street,  Minneapolis,  MN 55402-3796<BR>
Tel 612-343-2800  <B>*</B>  Fax 612-333-0066<BR>
