<BR>
<LI><B>Kent E. Mast</B> Complex litigation and all aspects of antitrust/trade regulation practice,  including mergers and acquisitions,  litigation,  federal and state investigations; civil and criminal enforcement proceedings; and counseling to achieve business objectives. Regularly active in matters concerning product distribution,  communications,  information compilation and dissemination,  and consumer protection.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Jerre B. Swann</B> Litigation of unfair trade practice and competition law matters,  including trademark and copyright protection,  unfair competition,  and antitrust.<BR>
<BR>
