<LI><B>Michael B. Terry</B> practices primarily in the area of business torts litigation and environmental litigation. University of Georgia,  B.A.,  <I>magna cum laude</I>,  1982,  J.D.,  <I>magna cum laude</I>,  1987; Order of the Coif; Order of Barristers; editorial board,  <I>Georgia Journal of International and Comparative Law</I>.<BR>
