Tel 813-222-8180  <B>*</B>  Fax 813-222-8189<BR>
<B>Lexington:</B> PNC Bank Plaza,  200 West Vine Street,  Suite 600,  Lexington,  KY 40507<BR>
Tel 606-225-5333  <B>*</B>  Fax 606-225-5334<BR>
