<P>
<P><B>F</B>iddler,  Gonzalez  & Rodriguez is a full-service law firm,  the oldest in Puerto Rico. Our litigation group works with members of our environmental,  tax,  banking,  labor,  finance,  and real estate groups as needed. All of the attorneys listed are fluent in English.
<P>
<CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Commercial Litigation Practice</H3></CENTER>

<P>Our commercial litigation practice includes representation of principals in dealer termination disputes,  of banks in lender liability actions,  and of insurers and brokers in coverage disputes,  as well as of both plaintiffs and defendants in disputes involving intellectual property,  contracts,  antitrust,  civil RICO,  and securities laws. The group also handles aviation,  products liability,  employment discrimination,  and environmental litigation.<BR>

<CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Clients and Experience</H3></CENTER>

