<CENTER>
<H2>Commercial Litigation</H2>
<H3>Honigman Miller Schwartz and Cohn
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Detroit:</B> 2290 First National Building,  Detroit,  MI 48226<BR>
