<P><BR>

<P>
<P><B>T</B>he lawyers of Kilpatrick  & Cody serve clients around the world from offices in Atlanta,  Augusta,  Washington,  D.C.,  London,  and Brussels. The hallmark of our service is our ability to develop cost-effective relationships with our clients relationships based on quality,  efficiency,  and teamwork to solve their problems and achieve their goals.
<P>
<CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Business Litigation</H3></CENTER>

<BR>
<P>We represent clients in civil litigation in state and federal courts,  and before administrative agencies throughout the United States. Our litigation section includes specialists in:<BR><UL><BR><LI>telecommunications<LI>construction disputes<LI>government contracts<LI>securities and business fraud<LI>antitrust and trade regulation<LI>products liability<LI>patent and trademark<LI>insurance coverage<LI>environmental<LI>zoning and land use<LI>white-collar criminal defense<LI>professional liability<BR></UL><BR>
<P>As markets and businesses have become global,  we have developed a special expertise in helping international businesses resolve disputes. We are skilled and experienced in domestic and international alternative dispute resolution,  including mediations and arbitrations administered by the American Arbitration Association,  the CPR Institute for Dispute Resolution,  the International Chamber of Commerce,  the London Court of International Arbitration,  and the World Intellectual Property Organization.<BR>
