<BR>
<LI><B>Elizabeth J. du Fresne</B> has extensive experience in class action defense and all aspects of employment and labor relations litigation,  representing both management and labor. She has tried more than 350 cases to jury and handled over 500 administrative discipline hearings.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Gerry S. Gibson</B> is the chairman of our litigation group in our West Palm Beach office. His practice emphasizes complex commercial litigation.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Thomas R. Julin</B> has served as chairman of the Florida Bar Media and Communications committee and concentrates his litigation practice in the defense of major media companies.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>William B. Killian</B> has more than 40 years' experience in Florida courtrooms,  concentrating in antitrust,  intellectual property and First Amendment matters.<BR>
