<LI><B>Lewis P. Murphy</B> is one of the most experienced securities litigators in Florida,  with a practice focusing on complex securities,  corporate control,  and fiduciary duty litigation.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Patricia A. Seitz</B> served as president of the Florida Bar in 1994 and is one of our most senior trial lawyers. Her trial practice focuses on franchise/distributor/manufacturer disputes,  including unfair trade practices,  and enforcement of rights involving third parties.
