<P>
<P>
<P>
<P><B>Z</B>uckerman,  Spaeder,  Goldstein,  Taylor  & Kolker (ZSGT &K) operates offices in five East Coast cities with a nationwide practice that emphasizes commercial litigation,  alternative dispute resolution through arbitration and other means,  and representation in government investigations and enforcement proceedings. The firm prides itself on the courtroom experience of its litigators,  who have served as counsel in hundreds of trials throughout the United States.
<P><BR><P>Representative business litigation clients of ZSGT &K have included the following: the Government of Argentina; Allegheny Beverage Corporation; The Bureau of National Affairs; CRI,  Inc.; Dart Group Corporation; Harris Corporation; Hellmann International Freight Forwarders,  Inc.; Intelsat; Kastle Systems,  Inc.; New York Life Insurance Company; NVR,  Inc.; the Oneida Indian Nation and its enterprises; PaineWebber,  Inc.; PHH,  Inc.; The Travelers Insurance Company.<BR><P>ZSGT &K litigation partners with at least 15 years of experience include:<BR>
