</UL>

<CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Miami</H3></CENTER>

<BR><BR><UL><LI><B>Ronald B. Ravikoff</B> heads the firm's office in Miami. His practice emphasizes federal commercial litigation,  primarily in the areas of antitrust,  unfair trade practices,  intellectual property,  securities,  financial institutions,  and the UCC.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Thomas J. Meeks</B> has litigated cases involving fraud and other forms of unfair dealing; securities arbitrations; real estate brokerage commission disputes; and construction litigation.<BR>
