<BR></UL><CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Tampa</H3></CENTER>
<BR><BR><UL><LI><B>Morris `Sandy' Weinberg,  Jr.</B> is a former assistant U.S. attorney in New York City who now heads the Tampa office of ZSGT &K. He has represented corporate clients in such matters as a civil False Claims Act dispute regarding a $300 million government contract; nationwide franchise/distributor fraud litigation; and securities,  civil RICO,  fraud,  and other business tort lawsuits.<BR>
<BR></UL>
