<LI><B>John D. Schupper</B> Experience in mergers and acquisitions,  principally in the banking area; public and private placements of equity and debt securities; development and implementation of business and negotiating strategies in leveraged buyouts and business takeovers; and general representation of broker-dealers.<BR>
