<LI><B>Allen B. Levithan</B> Experience in corporate,  partnership,  securities,  banking,  and thrift areas,  including representation of public and private corporations,  private investment partnerships,  banking and thrift institutions,  investment bankers,  underwriters,  investment advisors,  and other securities professionals.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>Peter H. Ehrenberg</B> Experience in securities and business law matters; representation of issuers and underwriters in the public offering of debt and equity securities; and participation in complex merger and acquisition transactions,  recapitalizations,  and ESOP financings.<BR>
