<LI><B>Alan Wovsaniker</B> Experience in business planning,  banking,  finance,  and securities regulation,  including initial funding and structuring of business organizations; planning and negotiating mergers,  business acquisitions and dispositions,  loans,  and other financings; and representation of issuers and underwriters in public and private securities offerings.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>George J. Mazin</B> Experience in real estate syndications and other private placements of securities,  public offerings of debt and equity securities,  investment company regulation,  organization and representation of limited partnerships,  mergers and acquisitions,  with emphasis on leveraged buyouts,  representation of borrowers and lenders in secured lending transactions,  and the purchase,  sale,  and financing of real estate.<BR>
