<BR>
<LI><B>Burton X. Rosenberg</B> (<I>Chicago</I>) is a business lawyer with a broad range of experience in financing matters,  handling everything from mergers and acquisitions to public offerings,  the formation of financial cooperatives,  and the formation of new ventures.<BR>
