<CENTER>
<H2>Environmental</H2>
<H3>Squire,  Sanders  & Dempsey
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Cleveland:</B> 4900 Society Center,  127 Public Square,  Cleveland,  OH 44114-1304<BR>
Tel 216-479-8500  <B>*</B>  Fax 216-479-8780<BR>
