<P>
<P><B>F</B>ounded in 1918,  Bronson,  Bronson  & McKinnon is a full-service law firm representing clients throughout the United States,  including emerging growth,  middle market,  and Fortune 500 businesses. Our Intellectual Property Group handles all types of litigation and transactional matters,  and offers comprehensive intellectual property application and prosecution,  counseling and licensing services. The Group's experience includes semiconductor design and manufacturing,  biotechnology,  computer software,  insurance,  video technology,  engineering,  medical products,  entertainment and business financings.<BR><BR><P>Representative intellectual property clients include Addison Design; Apple Computer Inc.; Advanced Micro Devices,  Inc.; Credence Systems Corp.; Federal Express Corp.; IBM; Keane,  Inc.; KLA Instruments; LifeScan Inc.; Pharmacia AB; Prologic Computer Corp.; Sebago Inc.; Teledyne Inc.; The Gunlocke Com-pany; Varian Associates Inc.; and Woodward-Clyde Consultants.<BR><P><I>Patent infringement actions including:</I><BR><UL><LI> Semiconductor manufacturing process and programmable logic devices<LI> Biotechnology process for purifying monoclonal antibodies (tried to verdict)<LI> SRAM and DAC circuitry for color video display technology (tried to verdict)<LI> Videotape recording<BR><BR></UL><P><I>Trademark/unfair trade actions including:</I><BR><UL><LI> Trademark and service mark infringement,  counterfeiting and `gray' marketing<BR><BR></UL><P><I>Copyright infringement actions including:</I><BR>
<UL><LI> Computer software
