<LI><B>Robert N. Phillips'</B> practice includes patent,  copyright,  maskwork,  and trademark litigation. Rob has represented an express courier company in a trademark infringement action. He also represented a shoe manufacturer in the prosecution of an unfair competition action.<BR>
