<BR>
<LI><B>Robert L. Baechtold</B> 25 years' experience in complex chemical,  pharmaceutical,  and biotech patent litigation as lead trial and appellate counsel. Interference and ITC practice. Former president,  New Jersey Patent Law Association; Board of Directors,  American Intellectual Property Law Association.<BR>
