<P>
<P>
<P><B>H</B>arness,  Dickey  & Pierce is one of the nation's largest intellectual property law firms,  operating globally since the 1920s. HD &P's attorneys have engineering or science degrees,  including mechanical,  electrical,  and chemical engineering; computer sciences; genetics; materials and metallurgical engineering; chemistry; physics; biochemistry; and agricultural engineering.
<P><BR><P>Representative clients include Chrysler Corporation,  LA-Z-BOY Chair Co.,  Procter  & Gamble,  Hughes Aircraft,  TRW,  Black  & Decker,  and Dow Chemical.<BR>
<UL><BR>
<LI><B>Charles H. Blair</B> has 35 years' experience in worldwide patent and trademark prosecution and licensing,  and managing huge portfolios of intellectual property.<BR>
