<BR>
<LI><B>Gerald J. Flintoft</B> Primarily litigation with some patent prosecution practice specializing in both biotechnology and chemical cases. Registered to practice before U.S. Patent and Trademark Office. Joined Pennie  & Edmonds,  1969. St. John's University,  B.S.,  chemistry,  <I>magna cum laude</I>,  1957; Georgetown University,  J.D.,  1964; Phi Delta Phi; editor,  <I>Georgetown Law Journal</I>,  1963-1964. Admitted in New York,  1965.<BR>
