<LI><B>William K. Konrad</B> specializes in the area of domestic and international patent prosecution for digital electronics,  semiconductor devices,  and microprocessor applications. University of Illinois at Urbana-Champagne,  B.S.,  computer engineering,  1974,  J.D.,  1977.<BR>
