<LI><B>W. Ronald Robins </B>practices in most areas of intellectual property law,  including litigation,  transactions involving the development and licensing of technology,  and trademark law. Lamar University,  B.S.,  chemical engineering,  1966; Univer-sity of Houston,  J.D.,  1969. Admitted in Texas,  1969.<BR>
