<BR>
<LI><B>Peter J. Hurtgen</B> (<I>Miami; 305-579-0350</I>) Mr. Hurtgen's practice concentrates in employment discrimination,  employee/employer relations,  OSHA and employee benefits law.<BR>
<BR>
<LI><B>William J. Flannery</B> (<I>Harrisburg; 717-237-4010</I>) Mr. Flannery's practice concentrates in collective bargaining,  public sector collective bargaining,  and public employment relations law.<BR>
