<H2>Product Liability</H2>
<H3>Chamberlain,  D'Amanda,  Oppenheimer  & Greenfield
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Rochester:</B> 1600 Crossroads Building,  Rochester,  NY 14614-1397<BR>
Tel 716-232-3730  <B>*</B>  Fax 716-232-3882<BR>
<BR>
28 lawyers  <B>*</B>  12 lawyers concentrating in litigation<BR>

