<LI><B>Roy Z. Rotenberg</B> practices in the areas of product liability,  insurance defense and commercial litigation. Recent cases have involved heavy equipment,  design of electronic equipment,  kerosene heaters,  and exploding bottles. He also heads the firm's collection practice. Syracuse University,  B.S.,  <I>cum laude</I>,  1982; State University of New York at Buffalo,  J.D.,  1985.
