<CENTER>
<H2>Product Liability</H2>
<H3>Goodsill Anderson Quinn & Stifel
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Honolulu:</B> Alii Place,  18th Floor,  1099 Alakea Street,  Honolulu,  HI 96813<BR>
