<P>
<P>
<P>
<P><B>G</B>oodsill Anderson Quinn  & Stifel,  one of Hawaii's oldest (1878) and largest law firms,  has a diversified practice with a full range of commercial and litigation services. Approximately half of the firm's attorneys are in the litigation section,  handling civil trials and appeals,  administrative proceedings,  arbitration,  alternative dispute resolution (ADR),  and claims investigation and evaluation. Goodsill attorneys have tried and taken through appeal a number of the most important reported Hawaii products liability cases. The firm is experienced in managing complex,  high-profile cases and has successfully defended claims arising from such products as motor vehicles,  medical products and devices,  prescription drugs,  chemicals,  asbestos,  aircraft,  construction equipment and materials,  athletic equipment,  and electrical equipment,  to name a few.
<P><BR><P>The firm serves as defense counsel for a number of insurance companies in coverage,  subrogation,  and bad faith claims,  and in actions brought against their insureds. These include high-exposure cases in a wide variety of areas.<BR><P>Representative clients: Aetna Life  & Casualty,  Beech Aircraft,  Ciba-Geigy, E. I. du Pont de Nemours  & Co.,  General Electric,  Kawasaki Motors,  Minnesota Mining  & Manufacturing,  McDonnell Douglas,  National Union Fire Insurance,  Pfizer,  Tokio Marine Management,  and U.S. Aviation Underwriters.<BR>
