<CENTER>
<H2>Product Liability</H2>
<H3>Goodwin,  Procter  & Hoar
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Boston:</B> Exchange Place,  Boston,  MA 02109<BR>
Tel 617-570-1000  <B>*</B>  Fax 617-523-1231<BR>
<B>Washington:</B> 901 Fifteenth Street,  N.W.,  Washington,  DC 20005<BR>
