<CENTER>
<H2>Product Liability</H2>
<H3>Lane PowellSpears Lubersky
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Seattle:</B> 1420 Fifth Avenue,  Suite 4100,  Seattle,  WA 98101<BR>
