<H2>Product Liability</H2>
<H3>Stites  & Harbison
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Louisville:</B> 1800 Providian Center,  Louisville,  KY 40202-3352<BR>
Tel 502-587-3400  <B>*</B>  Fax 502-587-6391<BR>
<B>Lexington:</B> 2300 Lexington Financial Center,  Lexington,  KY 40507<BR>
Tel 606-226-2300  <B>*</B>  Fax 606-253-9144<BR>
