<CENTER>
<H2>Product Liability</H2>
<H3>Vorys,  Sater, Seymour and Pease
</H3>

</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<B>Columbus:</B> 52 East Gay Street,  Columbus,  OH 43216<BR>
Tel 614-464-6400  <B>*</B>  Fax 614-464-6350  <B>*</B>  Home page: <A HREF="http://www.vssp.com">Home Page</A><BR>
