<P>
<CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Product Liability and Insurance Defense Practice</H3></CENTER>

<P>Wilmer,  Cutler  & Pickering has an experienced litigation practice consisting of lawyers who advise and represent clients in product liability and insurance defense matters. WC &P has represented clients in traditional product liability cases in addition to product liability matters that require an interdisciplinary approach. The firm has an extensive insurance coverage practice performing a broad range of litigation and counseling functions in connection with general liability and product liability,  as well as other forms of insurance. WC &P is one of five law firms designated by one of the largest groups of property and casualty insurers as national coverage counsel for complex insurance coverage disputes. The firm's practice is enhanced by state-of-the-art computer technology that enables its lawyers to work with vast amounts of information efficiently and effectively.<BR>

<CENTER><H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Experience and Clients</H3></CENTER>

<P><BR><BR>
